{"tid":634715,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片】近百港人疑墮內地「海岸居」買樓陷阱　每人涉款至少30萬人民幣","createTime":"2018-04-19T13:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T02:01:49.000Z","uid":73092,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b67fd58698219c7a3516e4b7c5c346781dd02c","tid":634715,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T13:05:53.000Z","msg":"一批在廣東省惠州惠東縣稔山鎮購買「海岸居」單位的港人，本月中接到清拆通知，每人涉及金額30萬元至40萬元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n「海岸居」屬「小產權房」，民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆表示，接獲80名港人求助，稱在內地購買後，才發現有關樓宇為只可用作村民自住的房屋，沒有國家簽發的土地使用證和預售許可證，買賣合同在有關部門沒有備案，交易不受法律認可；由於樓盤屬於違法建築，當局要求立即清拆。<br />\n<br />\n葛珮帆指出，現時有不少港人被內地人士游說，在不知情下購買這些價格較低的「小產權房」，在內地律師樓簽署文件的人亦僅為村民，出售方只有使用權，但沒有轉讓權。<br />\n<br />\n一年半前到惠州購買樓盤的馬先生表示，完成交易後有關部門稱樓盤屬於違建，並要求收樓即時清拆，自己亦收不到任何通知。"},{"pid":"e1653ccff9f420e2614f8d406b6360dfd045ade6","tid":634715,"uid":73092,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"岸居<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375b75c6d80ebfa134af2f122ded892393ebadfd","tid":634715,"uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e1653ccff9f420e2614f8d406b6360dfd045ade6","tid":634715,"uid":73092,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"岸居<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T13:08:24.000Z","msg":"hi岸居"},{"pid":"db0f39e69c977620453762063a1bb76c32d7fba6","tid":634715,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T13:09:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180419/s00001/1524121111057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2F1524121111057&d=odlsMY%2FUvJxbsnYOIisLTLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=8962e4e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180419%2Fs00001